MapsScraperAI is like a robot for scraping Bing Maps. It provides real and verified leads straight from Maps listings. One click gets local leads with AI power, including business names, addresses, photos, coordinates, websites, emails, social media, and more.

ğŸ”¹ Why use it
Scraping Bing Maps data has many benefits, including lead generation, research and data science, monitoring competition, and obtaining business contact details. It can help businesses understand customer needs, research competitors, and develop new strategies.

ğŸ”¹ Key Features
âœ“ Search and extract biz information from maps with the power of AI.
âœ“ Extract leads including business names, websites, email addresses, and social media profiles.
âœ“ Export data in Excel or CSV format.
âœ“ Batch search capability to search for multiple keywords simultaneously.

Manage repetitive tasks efficiently to maximize productivity throughout the day. More efficient than xx,xx,xx,xx

ğŸ”¹ How does it work
MapsScraperAI searches Bing Maps for business information, extracts all the information on each page, copies and pastes, and accesses the actual website for email address, city, country, etc. It finds the customer's location and email address on the last page of Bing Maps and exports it to a xls file.

ğŸ”¹ How to use it
â¤ Open your preferred web browser and install the chrome extension.
â¤ Search on map and enter your query.
â¤ Open "Maps Scraper AI" extension with a simple mouse click.
â¤ Download results in CSV or XLS file, with no limits on the amount of data you can export.

long.he:
MapsScraperAI is like a robot for scraping Bing Maps. It provides real and verified leads straight from Maps listings. One click gets local leads with AI power, including business names, addresses, photos, coordinates, websites, emails, social media, and more.

ğŸ”¹ Why use it
Scraping Bing Maps data has many benefits, including lead generation, research and data science, monitoring competition, and obtaining business contact details. It can help businesses understand customer needs, research competitors, and develop new strategies.

ğŸ”¹ Key Features
âœ“ Search and extract biz information from maps with the power of AI.
âœ“ Extract leads including business names, websites, email addresses, and social media profiles.
âœ“ Export data in Excel or CSV format.
âœ“ Batch search capability to search for multiple keywords simultaneously.

Manage repetitive tasks efficiently to maximize productivity throughout the day. More efficient than G Business Finder - G Map Leads Generation,G Maps Leads Finder - MapsLeads.net,Small Business Prospector

ğŸ”¹ How does it work
MapsScraperAI searches Bing Maps for business information, extracts all the information on each page, copies and pastes, and accesses the actual website for email address, city, country, etc. It finds the customer's location and email address on the last page of Bing Maps and exports it to a xls file.

ğŸ”¹ How to use it
â¤ Open your preferred web browser and install the chrome extension.
â¤ Search on map and enter your query.
â¤ Open "Maps Scraper AI" extension with a simple mouse click.
â¤ Download results in CSV or XLS file, with no limits on the amount of data you can export.

MapsScraperAI seperti robot untuk mengikis peta Bing. Ini memberikan arahan nyata dan terverifikasi langsung dari daftar peta. Satu klik mendapat petunjuk lokal dengan kekuatan AI, termasuk nama bisnis, alamat, foto, koordinat, situs web, email, media sosial, dan banyak lagi.

ğŸ”¹ Mengapa menggunakannya
Mengikis data Bing Maps memiliki banyak manfaat, termasuk pembuatan timbal, penelitian dan ilmu data, memantau persaingan, dan mendapatkan detail kontak bisnis. Ini dapat membantu bisnis memahami kebutuhan pelanggan, pesaing penelitian, dan mengembangkan strategi baru.

ğŸ”¹ Fitur utama
âœ“ Cari dan ekstrak informasi bisnis dari peta dengan kekuatan AI.

âœ“ Ekspor data dalam format Excel atau CSV.
âœ“ Kemampuan pencarian batch untuk mencari beberapa kata kunci secara bersamaan.

Kelola tugas berulang secara efisien untuk memaksimalkan produktivitas sepanjang hari. Lebih efisien dari LeadBoost - Linkedin Automation Software,IM Leads Extractor,Easy Scraper - Free Web Scraping,Get GroupLeads

ğŸ”¹ Bagaimana cara kerjanya
MapsScraperAI Pencarian Bing Maps Untuk Informasi Bisnis, Mengekstrak Semua Informasi di Setiap Halaman, Salinan dan Tempel, dan Mengakses Situs Web yang sebenarnya untuk Alamat Email, Kota, Negara, dll. Menemukan lokasi dan alamat email pelanggan di halaman terakhir Bing Maps dan mengekspornya ke file XLS.

ğŸ”¹ Cara menggunakannya
â¤ Buka browser web pilihan Anda dan instal ekstensi chrome.
â¤ Cari di peta dan masukkan kueri Anda.
â¤ Buka ekstensi "peta scraper ai" dengan klik mouse sederhana.
â¤ Hasil unduhan dalam file CSV atau XLS, tanpa batasan jumlah data yang dapat Anda ekspor.

long.sl:
MapsScraperAI is like a robot for scraping Bing Maps. It provides real and verified leads straight from Maps listings. One click gets local leads with AI power, including business names, addresses, photos, coordinates, websites, emails, social media, and more.

ğŸ”¹ Why use it
Scraping Bing Maps data has many benefits, including lead generation, research and data science, monitoring competition, and obtaining business contact details. It can help businesses understand customer needs, research competitors, and develop new strategies.

ğŸ”¹ Key Features
âœ“ Search and extract biz information from maps with the power of AI.
âœ“ Extract leads including business names, websites, email addresses, and social media profiles.
âœ“ Export data in Excel or CSV format.
âœ“ Batch search capability to search for multiple keywords simultaneously.

Manage repetitive tasks efficiently to maximize productivity throughout the day. More efficient than Simple B2B Leads,Leads2b - Busca de Contatos B2B - Stage,Indie Leads - Find B2B leads on Twitter for free,Free Google Maps Timeline Export to Excel,Place ID Finder for Google Maps

ğŸ”¹ How does it work
MapsScraperAI searches Bing Maps for business information, extracts all the information on each page, copies and pastes, and accesses the actual website for email address, city, country, etc. It finds the customer's location and email address on the last page of Bing Maps and exports it to a xls file.

ğŸ”¹ How to use it
â¤ Open your preferred web browser and install the chrome extension.
â¤ Search on map and enter your query.
â¤ Open "Maps Scraper AI" extension with a simple mouse click.
â¤ Download results in CSV or XLS file, with no limits on the amount of data you can export.

long.sw:
MapsScraperAI ni kama roboti ya kuchora ramani za Bing. Inatoa mwongozo halisi na uliothibitishwa moja kwa moja kutoka kwa orodha za ramani. Bonyeza moja hupata mwongozo wa ndani na nguvu ya AI, pamoja na majina ya biashara, anwani, picha, kuratibu, tovuti, barua pepe, media ya kijamii, na zaidi.

Kwa nini utumie
Takwimu za Ramani za Bing zina faida nyingi, pamoja na kizazi cha kuongoza, utafiti na sayansi ya data, mashindano ya ufuatiliaji, na kupata maelezo ya mawasiliano ya biashara. Inaweza kusaidia biashara kuelewa mahitaji ya wateja, washindani wa utafiti, na kukuza mikakati mpya.

Vipengele muhimu
Tafuta na toa habari ya biz kutoka ramani zilizo na nguvu ya AI.
âœ“ Dondoo inaongoza ikiwa ni pamoja na majina ya biashara, tovuti, anwani za barua pepe, na maelezo mafupi ya media ya kijamii.
âœ“ Takwimu za kuuza nje katika muundo wa Excel au CSV.
âœ“ Uwezo wa utaftaji wa kikundi kutafuta maneno mengi wakati huo huo.

Simamia kazi za kurudia vizuri ili kuongeza tija siku nzima. Ufanisi zaidi kuliko Email Finder by Leadzen.ai | Get B2B Contacts,Email Extractor: Unlimited B2B Leads Finder,Automated Inbox - Find Verified B2B Leads

ğŸ”¹ Inafanyaje kazi
MapsScraperAI hutafuta ramani za Bing kwa habari ya biashara, huondoa habari zote kwenye kila ukurasa, nakala na pastes, na hupata wavuti halisi kwa anwani ya barua pepe, jiji, nchi, nk Inapata eneo la mteja na anwani ya barua pepe kwenye ukurasa wa mwisho wa Ramani za Bing na kuiuza kwa faili ya XLS.

ğŸ”¹ Jinsi ya kuitumia
â¤ Fungua kivinjari chako cha wavuti unachopendelea na usakinishe kiendelezi cha Chrome.
Tafuta kwenye ramani na ingiza swala lako.
â¤ Fungua "Ramani Scraper AI" ugani na bonyeza rahisi ya panya.
